The [Shiny App](https://dcosme.shinyapps.io/explore-sca/) shows results from the preregistration described in the [preregistration example](@preregistration-example.qmd), which are a subset of analyses from a larger project.

Please select the **Longitudinal model comparison --> AIC curve** tab.
